<2ND_LINE>AM-Britain-Machete,0238</2ND_LINE>
<HEAD>Laughing Man Kills Child, Wounds Mother With Machete</HEAD>
<DATELINE>LONDON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A man wielding a machete attacked a woman pushing
her 18-month-old daughter in a stroller Monday in southeast London,
hacking the child to death and wounding the mother, police said.
   Scotland Yard said Monday it was questioning a 45-year-old man
in connection with the girl's death.
   The mother was treated at a hospital for head wounds, police
said. Their names were not released.
   A police spokeswoman said the woman was pushing her daughter in
a stroller along the balcony of their apartment when a man wielding
a 2-foot-long machete attacked them.
   The wounded mother fled screaming for help, said the
spokeswoman, speaking anonymously in keeping with British custom.
   ``The man then attacked the child who received fatal injuries,''
she said.
   Neighbor Julian Manning, 21, said he heard shouting and
screaming just after noon.
   ``I went outside and there was a woman running down the stairs
screaming,'' he said. ``The woman was hysterical and was screaming,
`My child, my child _ he has got my child!' The woman had blood
dripping from her hand and from her clothing.
   ``We could see the man the whole time. He was shouting, swearing
and laughing.''
   Manning said by the time police arrived, more than 30 people
were watching the killer, too frightened to approach him in case he
attacked again.
</TEXT>
